name: ice_cube_tray
description: Sterilite Ice Cube Tray 1-pk - White. The durable, yet flexible ice cube trays allows ice cubes to release with an easy twist. The ice trays stack securely without sticking and are designed to channel water so trays fill quickly. Each tray makes 16 nice-sized ice cubes. FLEXIBLE AND DURABLE: Ice cubes release easily with just a twist. STACKABLE: Trays stack easily and neatly in the freezer without sticking. Features: BPA-free. Material: Plastic. Care and Cleaning: Freezer Safe, Dishwasher-safe. Number of cavities: 16.
